      "content": "Here's a polished version of your abstract:\n\n\"This investigation excavates the empirical bounds of cognitive reasoning in artificial intelligence, exposing the intricate limitations that govern the performance of state-of-the-art models in navigating intricate thinking tasks. Through systematic analysis and modeling, we reveal the pronounced constraints that preclude AI system generalizability. Our findings underscore the pressing imperative of recognizing and addressing these cognitive limits in order to ensure the responsible development and deployment of artificial intelligence, thereby mitigating potential risks to human-critical decision-making processes.\"",
