      "role": "user",
      "content": "thanks, that sounds way better. one thing tho, i'm worried about the methodology section when i send this to the editors. they're gonna ask about how robust the study is, specifically regarding the participant sample size. how should we frame the sample size in the abstract so it doesn't look like a weakness but still fits that high-impact nature vibe?",
